               <msContents>
                  <summary>Homily on the Suffering of Our Lord by the Three Virgins, ድርሳነ ማኅየዊ, Psalter, ዳዊት፡</summary>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                    <locus from="ir" to="xxiiiv(erso)"/>
                    <title type="complete" ref="LIT1291Dersan"/>
                    <note>
                      arranged for the hours of the day (
                      introduction, <locus target="#iirv(erso)"/>";
                      evening, <locus from="iiv(erso)" to="viv(erso)"/>";
                      midnight, <locus from="viv(erso)" to="ixv(erso)"/>";
                      morning, <locus from="ixv(erso)" to="xiir(ecto)"/>";
                      third hour, <locus from="xiir(ecto)" to="xvr(ecto)"/>";
                      sixth hour, <locus from="xvr(ecto)" to="xviiir(ecto)"/>";
                      ninth hour, <locus from="xviiir(ecto)" to="xxir(ecto)"/>;
                      evening, <locus from="xxir(ecto)" to="xxiiiv(erso)"/>"
                    </note>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                      ...ድርሳነ።ሕማማቲሁ፡ ወሞቱ፡...።ዘጸሐፍዎ፡ ወንጌላውያን፡ ወሠላስ፡ ደናግል፡ በርዜዳ፡ ወመልተኢዳ፡ ወኤልሳቤጥ። ዘመሀሮን፡ እግዚእ፡ ምሥጢረ፡ ሕማማሂሁ። ወስሙ፡ ለዝንቱ፡ ድርሳን፡ ምሕየዊ።...
                    </incipit>
                  </msItem>

